reviewText:
Delivery was prompt.
  "Ancient Voices- Stonehenge" was completely lacking in scientific value.  I had purchased it to show to my seventh grade Geography class, and even the students saw it as quite poor.  It is full of production values with night time shots with plenty of smoke and back lighting.  Unfortunately, it contained almost none of the latest research, and instead speculated in the "Could it be" nonsense.
  This video is not worth buying.
